Package: CrimeAnalyticsPlatform
Title: India Crime Analytics and Prediction Dashboard
Version: 2.1.0
Date: 2026-06-07
Description: Enterprise-grade R Shiny dashboard for India crime intelligence.
    Covers 29 major cities (2020-2024). Provides data engineering, feature
    engineering (39 features), multi-model ML prediction (LR, RF, XGBoost-proxy),
    time-series forecasting ETS+ARIMA (2025-2030), SHAP-based XAI, 15
    statistical hypothesis tests (T/Chi-square/ANOVA), and an 11-section
    interactive dark-theme dashboard with automated Excel and HTML reporting.
    Fixed for Windows/Linux/Mac: all ASCII source code, UTF-8 safe.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2.0)
Imports:
    shiny (>= 1.7.0),
    shinycssloaders (>= 1.0.0),
    plotly (>= 4.10.0),
    DT (>= 0.28),
    dplyr (>= 1.1.0),
